            "text": "Fig. 1: Potential mechanisms of action of heparin in COVID-19. SARS-CoV-2, severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2; ACE2, angiotensin-converting enzyme 2; RAAS, renin-angiotensin-aldosterone system",
            "type": "figure"
        }
